{"tid":2287757,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"進步派逼宮 民主黨陷路線之爭","createTime":"2020-11-16T04:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T04:51:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"29780582495f7fb2e0c775e150544577b5135b23","tid":2287757,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201116/4WXWHY27H5HJ7KMB5MYB2RIRKA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201116%2F4WXWHY27H5HJ7KMB5MYB2RIRKA%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3lScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=746da9eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201116%2F4WXWHY27H5HJ7KMB5MYB2RIRKA%2F&h=3b1f44eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201116/4WXWHY27H5HJ7KMB5MYB2RIRKA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n進步派逼宮 民主黨陷路線之爭<br />\n<br />\n民主黨拜登打着反特朗普大旗，在大選期間成功團結左中右，如今共同敵人一去，黨內隨即掀起路線之爭：進步派不但要求拜登兌現左翼政綱承諾，甚至提倡全民健保及削減警隊經費等激進主張；溫和自由派則批評，正是因為走得太左，才令民主黨在國會選舉中失利。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：特朗普廢「追夢者」計劃受挫<br />\n<br />\n選後拜登要籌組班底執政，進步派在這場卡位戰最進取，繼精神領袖桑德斯自薦任勞工部長後，其智庫進步變革研究所日前更列出一份逾400名進步派專家名單讓拜登揀蟀，但同時警告他勿起用大企業代理人入閣。拜登至今僅公佈由兩派都接受的克萊恩任幕僚長。<br />\n<br />\n桑德斯的門生、前俄亥俄州參議員特納直言「民主黨有負黑人，有負年輕人，有負工人階級，這些人不是要回到常態才踢走特朗普，如果要他們繼續貧窮，常態根本無意思」。有意下屆問鼎總統大位的她警告「拜登若堅持中間路線」，民主黨勢必爆發內戰。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：不滿遭禁言 右派網上「移民」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CoKnO1wuF0arsrVJ3eXJxo0za20=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LDFLGZOZP5B5XDODNFMYQOSJU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCoKnO1wuF0arsrVJ3eXJxo0za20%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLDFLGZOZP5B5XDODNFMYQOSJU4.jpg&h=181693a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■拜登在亨洛彭角國家公園踩單車。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拜登踩單車減壓<br />\n<br />\n不過，拜登在選舉期間一直力抗極左主張， 縱橫政壇近半個世紀的他心知肚明，順從進步派或許會令民主黨避過一場內戰，但同時意味新政府未來四年將要跟右派的共和黨全面開戰，既違背他團結國家的願景，新內閣要在參議院取得確認任命也必困難重重。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/ 《華爾街日報》"},{"pid":"c107b54ce2265f8c38bddc6c1ae37df95c881dfd","tid":2287757,"uid":296369,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lawdog323/status/1328145585279365121?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flawdog323%2Fstatus%2F1328145585279365121%3Fs%3D21&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3lScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=600f0f41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flawdog323%2Fstatus%2F1328145585279365121%3Fs%3D21&h=67f5a5a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lawdog323/status/1328145585279365121?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nCongress 都出咗statement, 重未有President-elect, spread 出去各國祝賀Biden 嘅元首政客及fake news media....."},{"pid":"a92fb8d78c361b551ce3feeb9b8394146a2753ff","tid":2287757,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c458cbf17b85a56e0a4a1924b860ab4c7a4f0f","tid":2287757,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"進步派左膠要擁護共產黨"},{"pid":"ae9fc97ecb4be0d292408dafc1a1742fc7aaf089","tid":2287757,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"有時對蘋果真係又愛又恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a3b45c8bc6f0e3c5ae059a34a70f20f013f3ec","tid":2287757,"uid":77717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"進步派只是包裝過的共產黨，本質上係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hk